  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">tin "miseratio" is. And since mercy is an effect of charity , as shown above ( 30, 2, 3, Objection 3 ), it follows that almsgiving is an act of charity through the medium of mercy.</data>
